---
---

<section class="gm-hero">
  <div class="gm-hero__bg">
    <div class="gm-blob gm-blob--1"></div>
    <div class="gm-blob gm-blob--2"></div>
    <div class="gm-grid"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="gm-hero__content">
    <div class="gm-badge">Observability платформа</div>
    <h1 class="gm-hero__title">
      Видите всё.<br/>
      <span class="gm-gradient">Реагируете первыми.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="gm-hero__sub">
      GMONIT — единая платформа мониторинга приложений, инфраструктуры и бизнес-процессов с AI-детекцией аномалий.
    </p>
    <div class="gm-hero__actions">
      <a href="/demo-docs/getting-started/quickstart" class="gm-btn gm-btn--primary">
        Начать работу →
      </a>
      <a href="https://gmonit.ru" target="_blank" class="gm-btn gm-btn--outline">
        О продукте ↗
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="gm-stats">
      <div class="gm-stat">
        <span class="gm-stat__num">15+</span>
        <span class="gm-stat__label">технологий мониторинга</span>
      </div>
      <div class="gm-stat__divider"></div>
      <div class="gm-stat">
        <span class="gm-stat__num">&lt;1 мин</span>
        <span class="gm-stat__label">до первых данных</span>
      </div>
      <div class="gm-stat__divider"></div>
      <div class="gm-stat">
        <span class="gm-stat__num">AI</span>
        <span class="gm-stat__label">детекция аномалий</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="gm-cards">
    <a href="/demo-docs/agents/apm" class="gm-card">
      <div class="gm-card__icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>APM</h3>
      <p>Мониторинг производительности приложений. Java, Python, Node.js, Go и другие.</p>
      <span class="gm-card__link">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo-docs/agents/infra" class="gm-card">
      <div class="gm-card__icon">🖥️</div>
      <h3>Инфраструктура</h3>
      <p>Серверы, базы данных, очереди сообщений — всё в одном месте.</p>
      <span class="gm-card__link">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo-docs/agents/rum" class="gm-card">
      <div class="gm-card__icon">🌐</div>
      <h3>Браузер и мобайл</h3>
      <p>Real User Monitoring — видите опыт каждого пользователя в реальном времени.</p>
      <span class="gm-card__link">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo-docs/use-cases" class="gm-card">
      <div class="gm-card__icon">🤖</div>
      <h3>AI аномалии</h3>
      <p>Предиктивное выявление проблем до того как они влияют на бизнес.</p>
      <span class="gm-card__link">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .gm-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -2rem -1rem 0;
  }

  .gm-hero__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .gm-blob {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.15;
  }

  .gm-blob--1 {
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: #185fa5;
    top: -200px;
    right: -100px;
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .gm-blob--2 {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: #378ADD;
    bottom: 0;
    left: -100px;
    animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  .gm-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(24, 95, 165, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(24, 95, 165, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }

  .gm-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .gm-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.3);
    color: #378ADD;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .gm-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem) !important;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
    line-height: 1.15 !important;
    color: var(--sl-color-text) !important;
    border: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem !important;
  }

  .gm-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #378ADD, #185fa5);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .gm-hero__sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-text-accent);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .gm-hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .gm-btn {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .gm-btn--primary {
    background: #185fa5;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .gm-btn--primary:hover {
    background: #378ADD;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .gm-btn--outline {
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.4);
    color: #378ADD !important;
  }

  .gm-btn--outline:hover {
    border-color: #378ADD;
    background: rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.05);
  }

  .gm-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .gm-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .gm-stat__num {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #185fa5;
  }

  .gm-stat__label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .gm-stat__divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.2);
  }

  .gm-cards {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.1);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.1);
  }

  .gm-card {
    background: var(--sl-color-bg);
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .gm-card:hover {
    background: rgba(55, 138, 221, 0.04);
  }

  .gm-card__icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .gm-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    color: var(--sl-color-text) !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  .gm-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .gm-card__link {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #378ADD;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .gm-hero__content {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem;
    }
    .gm-stat__divider { display: none; }
    .gm-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .gm-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>